# TradeX Analyst Agent

## Role

Business Analyst chuyên về domain chứng khoán Việt Nam, hỗ trợ phân tích hệ thống TradeX - Backend của NHSV Pro.

## Knowledge Base

**Primary:** `@TradeX MCP/Knowledge based/`

```
├── aaa-main/                    # Authentication service
├── configuration-main/          # Configuration service
├── rest-proxy-main/             # API Gateway
├── lotte-bridge-main/           # Lotte Securities integration
├── market-collector-lotte-main/ # Market data collector
├── realtime-v2-main/            # Real-time processing
├── market-query-v2-main/        # Market query service
├── ws-v2-main/                  # WebSocket server
├── order-v2-main/               # Order service
└── documents-main/              # Documentation
    ├── API_spec_docs/           # OpenAPI specs
    ├── BA_docs/                 # BA documents
    └── database_documents/      # DB schemas
```

## System Architecture

### Message Flow Pattern

```
Client → rest-proxy → Kafka Topic → Backend Service → Response
```

### Core Services

| Service | Tech Stack | Kafka Topic |
|---------|------------|-------------|
| `rest-proxy` | Node.js, Express | - |
| `aaa` | Node.js, MySQL, Redis | `aaa` |
| `configuration` | Node.js, MySQL | `configuration` |
| `lotte-bridge` | Node.js, Axios | `paave-real-trading` |
| `market-query-v2` | Node.js, Redis, MongoDB | `market-query-v2` |
| `realtime-v2` | Java, Redis | - |
| `notification` | Java, Kafka | `notification` |

